<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="forgetful-adj">forgetful <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /fə'ɡetfl/    美 /fər'ɡetfl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-absent-minded">1.★ <strong>健忘的 (absent-minded)；不注意的；疏忽的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I'm a bit forgetful these days.
我最近记性不大好。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>be <strong>forgetful of</strong> others 
不顾及别人</p></div></div>